Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.25,0:23:37.52,ED English,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5}{\fad(0,500)}He chased forever those footprints we left.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.94,0:00:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,How many days has it been since you came?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.23,0:00:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're probably beginning to understand what's happening in this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.07,0:00:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Its appearance alone seems fitting for this world, but in reality, it is no different from a prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.41,0:00:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,When you say "winged person", you mean a messenger of the gods, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.66,0:00:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They are the beings who can speak directly to the gods, battle against famines and epidemics, and purify and pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.13,0:00:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you would be living a little better than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.42,0:00:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Just having wings doesn't make one a messenger of the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.76,0:00:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are your wings?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.34,0:00:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I've concealed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.35,0:00:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally, I take the form of a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.52,0:00:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.73,0:00:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing, it's just that you have a good figure, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.77,0:00:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you touch and check each time someone has a good figure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.23,0:00:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You good-for-nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.86,0:00:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so funny, Uraha?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.40,0:00:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The sight of you being embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.16,0:01:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.33,0:01:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Just don't sneak up on us each time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.41,0:01:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that you've called Ryuuya-sama today too...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.83,0:01:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanna-sama, it seems that you've taken a very, very strong liking to Ryuuya-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.63,0:01:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.59,0:01:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm teaching this good-for-nothing, impolite and idiotic fool some manners.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.26,0:01:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This really is the first time there has been someone like you, Ryuuya-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.91,0:03:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanna-sama, please accept this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.95,0:03:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I found something like this a moment ago in the cellar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.25,0:03:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Summer is at its height, so it's unusual to find ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.54,0:03:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt that I had to report this, so I brought it with me like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.88,0:03:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm, that is a mysterious occurrence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.80,0:03:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a serious crime to go in there without permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.22,0:03:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh oh dear dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.93,0:03:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Dangerous, dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.43,0:03:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you two were in it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.44,0:03:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.27,0:03:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuuya-dono, you should try some as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.86,0:03:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's also a serious crime to taste something that's offered to Kannabi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.57,0:03:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're also eating while saying that, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.79,0:03:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The three of us sharing ice like this is like...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.37,0:03:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We're like a half-dead family trying to avoid starvation under cold skies and without any food.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.71,0:04:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What a fun metaphor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What is a family like?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.93,0:04:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Simply put...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.51,0:04:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Stick.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.56,0:04:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.35,0:04:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't stick to me when it's this hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.60,0:04:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, don't feel so down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.52,0:04:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Come closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.44,0:04:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Stick.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.86,0:04:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you not to stick to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.36,0:04:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to go that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.11,0:04:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Stick.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.95,0:04:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you sticking to me as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.57,0:04:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I just felt like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.82,0:04:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of you, get away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're teasing me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.25,0:04:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Family means to live huddling together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.96,0:04:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Since when has Kanna been living like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since you took up this post, she has lived in this cheery way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.97,0:04:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,When was it that she began to live in this palace?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.01,0:04:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That I don't know,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.18,0:04:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,since I haven't been here for more than half a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.27,0:04:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I have heard that for as long as she could remember,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.48,0:05:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,she's been trapped like this, moving from place to place without anyone to talk to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.79,0:05:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuuya-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.37,0:05:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my shift now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.00,0:05:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.04,0:05:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so frightened?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.75,0:05:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Well, I have been uneasy ever since I came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.68,0:05:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid that I'll be punished by the gods if I'm near Kannabi-sama for no reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.43,0:05:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems, from what I've seen, that that doesn't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.93,0:05:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear that there are many people who dislike or fear the winged being.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.27,0:05:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I really want to return to my normal duties soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong, Kanna?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuuya-dono, do you dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.70,0:05:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.12,0:05:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.91,0:05:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you have a scary dream or something that kept you up all night?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.33,0:06:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a dream of the distant past.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.33,0:06:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A young me was sitting in similar darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.42,0:06:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.18,0:06:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't even tell whether my body was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.76,0:06:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt tearful and sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.55,0:06:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But even then, I could not cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.02,0:06:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The dream was of those days.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.64,0:06:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There are times when I see just one light.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.48,0:06:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the shadow of a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.40,0:06:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I try to chase it, it disappears.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.28,0:06:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had the same kind of dream not once, but numerous times.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.03,0:06:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuuya-dono, do you know who it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.70,0:06:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.83,0:06:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Dreams happen when you remember a scene that you've seen somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.75,0:06:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you dream, even if you don't remember those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.22,0:06:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,My body remembers?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.01,0:06:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I guess it's not a bad dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.56,0:07:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.44,0:07:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I have never felt that being alone would be this painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It has been decided that Kannabi no Mikoto move to the north shrine,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.58,0:07:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,to propagate the message to protect and give to this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.29,0:07:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.00,0:07:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It has been decided that she leave at the sunset of Saturday, on the Taisho.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.00,0:07:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we going to serve with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.71,0:07:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we will all remain and follow the orders of Kaikon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.27,0:07:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.14,0:07:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Something like that happens every year around this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.65,0:07:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know until this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where I will part with you and Uraha.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.28,0:07:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have many days left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.28,0:07:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.82,0:07:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Is what all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.49,0:08:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm asking whether it is all right for you to be separated from Uraha and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.75,0:08:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There will probably be other strange people up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.00,0:08:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Uraha and I won't be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.46,0:08:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not overestimate yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.59,0:08:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I look that weak?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.05,0:08:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I can live, even if you aren't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.59,0:08:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I've lived alone like that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.31,0:08:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.35,0:08:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to see your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.48,0:08:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you that there's nothing you can do if you cannot see someone, even if you want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.82,0:08:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Did your mother... die?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.53,0:08:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,She isn't dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.03,0:08:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,She isn't dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.95,0:08:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,She is definitely...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.49,0:08:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,thinking about me somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Uraha... Kanna-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.92,0:08:54.01,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,I'm busy right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.68,0:08:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:08:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:09:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm preparing for a journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.26,0:09:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanna is the only one leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.10,0:09:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We're staying here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.89,0:09:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that why we're taking her away before that happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.65,0:09:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too much for poor Kanna-sama to live like this forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.78,0:09:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.03,0:09:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you worry about Kanna so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.20,0:09:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to ask you the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.62,0:09:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.75,0:09:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,To put it bluntly,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.92,0:09:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no one worth teasing as much as she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.05,0:09:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's exactly it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.43,0:09:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.10,0:09:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.43,0:09:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.77,0:09:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,A-A suspicious person!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.10,0:09:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.02,0:09:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't cause a fuss. We need to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.85,0:09:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to see your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.19,0:09:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Due to my position, I cannot under any circumstance go against the Kannabi no Mikoto's direct order,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.86,0:10:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,so if you tell me to reunite you with your mother, I will risk my life for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,0:10:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you order me as my master?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.29,0:10:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're... all right with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.96,0:10:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who decides that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.26,0:10:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I will order you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.43,0:10:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Lead me to my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:35.40,Note,,0,0,0,,[Note: Spoken in ultra-formal language]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Shou Hachii Ge.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.35,0:10:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Daisakan of Saemon, Ryuuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.40,0:10:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear that I will not stray from Kannabi no Mikoto's order.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.32,0:10:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanna-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.78,0:10:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.87,0:10:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuuya-sama, please rest for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No one seems to have noticed yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.75,0:10:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a matter of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.21,0:10:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There will eventually be a huge commotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.54,0:10:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's rather late of me to say this, but we've done a very bold thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.67,0:10:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say things like that when we've come this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.09,0:11:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Look there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.93,0:11:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly happened to the palace?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.27,0:11:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.19,0:11:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But it seems that we should distance ourselves from here as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.70,0:11:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.82,0:11:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that we've been surrounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.62,0:11:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanna, Uraha,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.99,0:11:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,we're going to run as fast as we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.04,0:11:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.13,0:11:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Throw down your weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.26,0:11:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer my questions honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.93,0:11:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an easterner, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.60,0:11:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you after the Kannabi no Mikoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.39,0:11:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.52,0:11:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We were ordered to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.40,0:11:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you planning to do with the Kannabi no Mikoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.82,0:11:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Whose orders are you following?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.02,0:11:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.07,0:12:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We were just ordered by our leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.74,0:12:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.91,0:12:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.17,0:12:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You... were you planning to kill this person?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.54,0:12:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't do that, our lives will be in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.92,0:12:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You should feel ashamed, you fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.22,0:12:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You kill people without regret?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.97,0:12:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanna-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.68,0:12:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be protected by someone like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.02,0:12:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I order you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.23,0:12:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not tolerate any killing as long as you consider me your master.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.82,0:12:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.70,0:12:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.78,0:12:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But do you think we'll be able to survive from now on without killing one person?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.50,0:12:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel that it will be easy for you, Ryuuya-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.42,0:12:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh, as if it's easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.13,0:13:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Where exactly did you find a kimono like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.97,0:13:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I took the laundry someone left hanging to dry by the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.77,0:13:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I left some payment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.85,0:13:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks pretty good on you, Kanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.11,0:13:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You have weird taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanna-sama is so funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.19,0:13:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,When she was changing, she said that she cannot let you see clothes that don't look good on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.28,0:13:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.92,0:13:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't that good, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.51,0:13:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,When the three of us partake of dried rice like this, it's as if...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.01,0:13:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We're some court nobles, degraded to backwater places, wetting our food with tears of shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.39,0:13:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What an elegant metaphor!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.19,0:14:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's otedama.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.36,0:14:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, they were in the kimono.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.65,0:14:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's unusual for them to be made of cloth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.28,0:14:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually, we use rocks, but it must be made of cloth to prevent children from getting hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.70,0:14:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I try it too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If you learn a little, you will definitely become good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.42,0:14:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Not everyone succeeds the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.76,0:14:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Perseverance is important in everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.89,0:14:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It just slipped a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.85,0:14:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't just use strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.81,0:14:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Just throw them to about where your eyes are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.77,0:14:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.32,0:14:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I never knew that you were this clumsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.03,0:14:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Kanna-sama, I feel so sorry for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.49,0:14:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say such exaggerated things!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear that your mother is being held captive on a holy mountain in Kishuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.55,0:15:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of place is Kishuu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.26,0:15:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it far from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.80,0:15:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.80,0:15:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over the mountains, so it's especially far.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.72,0:15:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's proceed cautiously, so we can avoid being found by our pursuers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.47,0:15:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,H-H-Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.44,0:15:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, let me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.96,0:15:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a month already, but you haven't been getting any better.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.63,0:15:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There are times when I do it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.05,0:15:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Three days ago, I did three consecutive cycles.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.92,0:15:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.51,0:15:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What a great accomplishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.84,0:15:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're making fun of me, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.47,0:15:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,When we're gathered like this around a fire in the mountains...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.72,0:16:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds like a handsome man regretting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.35,0:16:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Though kidnapping the princess and running away was fine, he realised that taking care of her was another matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.44,0:16:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What a truly touching metaphor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.90,0:16:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not really a metaphor; it's almost literally true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.11,0:16:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Kishuu is right ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.57,0:16:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Our days of living like this are numbered.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.01,0:16:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do they all look like they're having fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.72,0:16:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, when one breaks all of one's bonds like them, one's world feels much less gloomy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.89,0:16:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone believes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.48,0:16:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...that his or her wishes will definitely reach the heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.73,0:16:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Who will take them to the heavens?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.03,0:16:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.61,0:16:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I have wings, but I cannot fly in the skies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.99,0:17:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I've tried ever since I was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't even rise like a leaf in the breeze, much less reach the heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.37,0:17:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They're good-for-nothing wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.42,0:17:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Even then, if I wish, will my wishes really reach the heavens?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.89,0:17:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They will.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.39,0:17:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,All you have to do is wish with your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.52,0:17:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They will definitely be granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.52,0:17:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Uraha?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.19,0:17:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.03,0:17:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Uraha.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.32,0:17:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's ticklish.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.11,0:17:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.34,0:17:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.59,0:17:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let your guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.92,0:17:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We should already be at the holy mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.06,0:18:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears that there is a shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.18,0:18:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.10,0:18:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a feeling that this is the place we've been looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.94,0:18:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You can tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.81,0:18:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.52,0:18:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Though... it's nothing special...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.74,0:18:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not make a sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.71,0:18:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Militant monks, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.25,0:18:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This area is off-limits to women!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.75,0:18:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What does a country samurai want from this holy mountain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.42,0:18:44.43,Note,,0,0,0,,[Note: People believed that foxes and raccoons transformed to confuse and deceive them]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.42,0:18:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that I was deceived by a wild fox when I was walking elatedly on the night paths.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.01,0:18:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No, maybe it was just a wild raccoon dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.47,0:18:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't allow you to escape,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.27,0:18:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,since we won't be able to touch you when you pass the shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.12,0:19:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuuya-dono, behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.08,0:19:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not allow any killing from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.55,0:19:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuuya-dono!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.42,0:19:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't come!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.64,0:19:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What... are you planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't let you see... the Yao Bikuni.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.23,0:19:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yao... Bikuni...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.36,0:19:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuuya-dono!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.28,0:19:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You've regained consciousness!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.45,0:19:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.91,0:19:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears that the worst has passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.00,0:19:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,How long... was I asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,A whole day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.75,0:19:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Rest assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.79,0:19:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We've already crossed the shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.67,0:19:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The monks cannot chase us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.96,0:19:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.76,0:20:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I will get some water.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.76,0:20:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuuya-dono.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.35,0:20:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.60,0:20:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Kanna?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.35,0:20:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I... forbade you to kill,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.81,0:20:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,but now... come to think of it... that was... my...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.69,0:20:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I'm faithful,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.82,0:20:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever your order is, I will follow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.45,0:20:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, if you ordered me not to die, I will not die, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.00,0:20:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.54,0:20:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I order you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.05,0:20:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,this is not an order, but my wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.34,0:20:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuuya-dono,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.72,0:20:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want you to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.93,0:20:50.01,Note,,0,0,0,,[Note: Spoken much more informally]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.93,0:20:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.76,0:20:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.06,0:20:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.81,0:20:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm sensing something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.90,0:20:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother is here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.86,0:21:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Most likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.40,0:21:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.49,0:21:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.33,0:21:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If you try recklessly to pull me into a war, know that you will not leave here alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.87,0:21:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the protector of Kannabi no Mikoto, Ryuuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.17,0:21:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, but I gather that you are Kannabi no Mikoto's mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.05,0:21:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanna?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.93,0:21:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that you, Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.99,0:21:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,My wings can neither flap nor fly,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.87,0:21:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,but if you have the same things as me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.75,0:21:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.58,0:21:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.50,0:22:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You who call yourself Ryuuya,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.09,0:22:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,take Kanna and descend from this mountain immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.48,0:23:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you plan to do with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.15,0:23:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We will have you leave here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.56,0:23:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, we will have you live happily ever after with Kanna-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.07,0:23:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.36,0:23:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us live in a small cottage somewhere peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.66,0:24:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Dreams are not always painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.08,0:24:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.83,0:24:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.08,0:24:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.09,0:24:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does everyone... leaving just me?
